    "This standardized framework facilitates collaboration, coordination, cooperation, and communication among stakeholders engaged in DT simulation models.",
    "BSIC aims to establish a shared platform for selecting and integrating various simulation models to enhance the effectiveness of DT simulations.",
    "Because this study is based solely on the Scopus and Web of Science databases, some publications on factors affecting DT implementation in buildings may not have been included.",
    "Therefore, this research may not comprehensively represent all available literature on this topic.",
    "In addition, although significant publications were carefully selected, some specific keywords may have been overlooked in the literature search."
